        {
            "title": "AEON信貸全年純利增長16.9% 末期息增至每股0.33元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">AEON信貸(00900)公布，截至今年2月底止年度，公司擁有人應佔溢利4.68億元，按年升16.9%；擬派末期息增至每股0.33元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：AEON信貸官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240626_FI_source-web_00900-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：AEON信貸官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240626_FI_source-web_00900-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：AEON信貸官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">計入已派中期息0.25元，全年度每股共派0.58元，派付股息比率達51.9%；全年每股派息也較對上年度的0.49元提升18.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內公司收入18.25億元，按年升3.8%。淨利息收入14.17億元，按年增5.2%。減值虧損及減值準備降至4.22億元，按年減5.5%，佔收入比率亦降至23.1%，按年降2.3個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15817271-aeon%e4%bf%a1%e8%b2%b8%e5%85%a8%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b716-9-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e5%a2%9e%e8%87%b3%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a10-33%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240626_FI_source-web_00900-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-31 12:53:41",
            "source": "bastillepost",
