            "title": "保利置業溢利及末期息升逾23%  三條紅線指標進入綠檔",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">保利置業(00119)公布，截至2025年12月31日股東應佔溢利為2.25億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年升23.16%，每股基本盈利為5.89分。派發末期股息每股2.6港仙，較2024年度2.1港仙增加23.81%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"保利置業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/00119-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"保利置業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/00119-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">保利置業官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">收入483.82億元，按年升20.33%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公布稱，集團負債結構持續優化。經營性現金淨流入為35.56億元，總現金佔總資產比率17.1%。三條紅線指標正式進入綠檔，平均融資成本下降至2.86%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15817195-%e4%bf%9d%e5%88%a9%e7%bd%ae%e6%a5%ad%e6%ba%a2%e5%88%a9%e5%8f%8a%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be23-%e4%b8%89%e6%a2%9d%e7%b4%85%e7%b7%9a%e6%8c%87%e6%a8%99%e9%80%b2%e5%85%a5%e7%b6%a0",
